(a) **Refuted as the cause.** There is no `setActive(true)` reactivation in the same `SpaceEnvironment`, but the main claim misses scene rebuild.

In-space hyperspace lifecycle:
- `CM_aboutToHyperspace` creates `new HyperspaceIoWin(..., S_enter)` in [PlayerCreatureController.cpp](/D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clientGame/src/shared/controller/PlayerCreatureController.cpp:1995).
- `HyperspaceIoWin` sets `s_playHyperspaceBeforeSceneChange = true` for `S_enter` and queues `CockpitStage` + `ThirdPersonStage` in [HyperspaceIoWin.cpp](/D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clientGame/src/shared/core/HyperspaceIoWin.cpp:959).
